venues.parkingDetail: Grand Canal Square car park, managed by Q-Park is open, to reserve parking visit www.q-park.ie. Customers are advised to pre-book their parking spaces. Access to Grand Canal Square’s car park is on Chimney View, just off Pearse Street. There is also limited on street parking. The Convention Centre Car Park is located underground at the Convention Centre. Once parked at the Convention Centre customers can access the BGE Theatre via a short walk across the Samuel Beckett Bridge. Details on the exact entrance to car park and exit locations can be found at www.theccd.ie/parking. Entrance to the car park is from 5pm onwards and a pre-booked ticket is valid from 5pm to midnight. Other car parks are available at: Connolly Station, the NCI, Dawson Street and Setanta place (off Nassau Street) or visit: www.aaroadwatch.ie
